esmanager (1.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Implemented support of new index which iOS mod's contains too
  * Implemented mod's folder customization for Android
  * Implemented renpy traceback and log displaying and copying to clipboard
  * Implemented Installation/deletion statistics sending
  * Implemented autosearch mod's and trace's folders on iOS
  * Implemented launch-screen displaying while loading
  * Many bugfixes, GUI and internal algorithms improvements

 --  Alexander S. Salieff <salieff@mail.ru>  Sun, 28 Feb 2016 03:45:54 +0300

