esmanager (0.6-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * GUI redesigned with point-metrics and DPI calculations. Fonts and icons have same physical sizes on various screens as result
  * Implemented files overwrite request
  * Improved GUI responsibility
  * Disk operations isolated in separate thread to avoid GUI freezes
  * Now application have name - ES Mod Installer (org.salieff.esmodinstaller) and icon

 --  Alexander S. Salieff <salieff@mail.ru>  Mon, 21 Dec 2015 22:16:00 +0300

